Section 3.3: address_space_translate

The Translation Pipeline

```
Guest Physical Address (GPA)
    ↓
address_space_translate()
    ↓
1. Find MemoryRegion (via FlatView)
2. Compute offset within region
3. If IOMMU: translate again
4. If alias: follow alias
5. If RAM: return host pointer
6. If MMIO: return region + offset
    ↓
Host Virtual Address (HVA) or MemoryRegion + offset
```

Code Walkthrough

```c
// system/physmem.c

MemoryRegion *flatview_translate(FlatView *fv, hwaddr addr, hwaddr *xlat,
                                 hwaddr *plen, bool is_write,
                                 MemTxAttrs attrs) {
    // 1. Find FlatRange covering addr
    for (int i = 0; i < fv->nr; i++) {
        FlatRange *fr = &fv->ranges[i];
        if (addr >= fr->start && addr < fr->start + fr->size) {
            // 2. Compute offset within region
            *xlat = addr - fr->start + fr->offset;
            *plen = fr->size - (addr - fr->start);
            
            // 3. Check IOMMU
            if (fr->mr->iommu_ops) {
                return iommu_translate(fr->mr, *xlat, plen, is_write, attrs);
            }
            
            // 4. Check alias
            if (fr->mr->alias) {
                return alias_translate(fr->mr, xlat, plen);
            }
            
            // 5. Return region
            return fr->mr;
        }
    }
    
    return NULL;
}
```

