Section 5.1: Beyond the FlatView

The Scalability Problem

Challenge: FlatView computation O(N) where N = number of MemoryRegions. With 10,000 VMs and 100 regions each = 1M regions.

Solution: Hierarchical FlatViews (per-VM, per-device).

```c
