1. Caching: Use MRU cache and per-IOThread caches
2. Huge pages: Reduce TLB misses (2MB pages)
3. Pre-translation: Translate once, cache for bulk I/O
4. IOThreads: Separate address spaces per thread
5. Bypass: Use memory_region_get_ram_ptr() for RAM
6. Result: <100ns translation latency

</details>

